snippet.title: Syberia 3 | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
"Syberia 3" is a continuation to the Syberia series, which contains steampunk elements and follows the adventures of ex-lawyer Kate Walker as she travels across Eastern Europe. This trailer includes artworks and a brief look into the setting.
